  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA285-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu tōḻi ciṟaippuṟamākat talaimakaṭkuc colluvāḷāyat talaimakaṉ kēṭpa “vampalum alarum āyiṟṟu” eṉṟu colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante said, as one who speaks to HER, so that HE would hear when [he] was behind the fence “there has been scandal and gossip.”</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA285">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            aravirai tēru māriru ṇaṭunā</l>
<l>            ḷiraviṉ varuta laṉṟiyu muravukkaṇai</l>
<l>            vaṉkaik kāṉavaṉ veñcilai vaṇakki</l>
<l>            yuḷamicait tavirtta muḷavumā ṉēṟṟaiyoṭu</l>
<l>            maṉaivāy ñamali yoruṅkupuṭai yāṭa </l>
<l>            vēṭṭuvalam paṭutta vuvakaiyaṉ kāṭṭa</l>
<l>            naṭukāṟ kurampaittaṉ kuṭivayiṟ peyaruṅ</l>
<l>            kuṉṟa nāṭaṉ kēṇmai namakkē</l>
<l>            naṉṟāl vāḻi tōḻi yeṉṟu</l>
<l>            mayalō rampali ṉakalāṉ </l>
<l>            pakaliṉ varūu meṟipuṉat tāṉē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The intimacy with the man from a land of hills,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the strong-handed forest man with strong arrow bends</l>
<l rend="indent">[his] cruel bow</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] comes back to his home, a hut on erect stilts,</l>
<l rend="indent2">to show himself joyful as the hunting had been successful<note place="foot">This might be just about a way of construing line 6: unless we accept <term xml:lang="ta">uvakaiyaṉ</term> there is no direct object for <term xml:lang="ta">kāṭṭa</term>. Another way might be an emendation of <term xml:lang="ta">paṭutta</term> into <term xml:lang="ta">paṭuttal</term> (which could be easily explained as a textual corruption, since the graphemes for l and v are so similar).</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent3">while the dogs play together in a site at the house,</l>
<l rend="indent3">with a male of the porcupine hit(?) in the breast,</l>
<l rend="indent">who, besides coming at night,</l>
<l rend="indent2">at midnight by difficult darkness when the snake searches for prey,</l>
<l rend="indent">comes at midday to the field shielded [by us],</l>
<l rend="indent">not one to leave off because of the rumours among the neighbours,</l>
<l>daily, for us it [is] good indeed, oh friend.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
